	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Review: Dawn of War Beta</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin Darkeyes</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug 25, 2004, 06:05</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Review%3A%20Dawn%20of%20War%20Beta&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_27.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
